<br>
<b>Free Peoples (39+Starting Gandalf) </b><br>
Aragorn, Heir to the White City x3 <br>
Legolas Greenleaf x2<br>
Gimli, Dwarf of the Mountain-race x2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(307)">Boromir, Son of Denethor</a><br>
